OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOrkney will be cloudy with rain
OL,6,Fat times, occasionally heavy. Dry
OL,7,Facross Shetland with variable amounts
OL,8,Fof cloud and some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShetland may see a little
OL,12,Flight rain at times this evening,
OL,13,Fotherwise dry. Cloudy across Orkney
OL,14,Fwith some rain and drizzle. A chilly
OL,15,Fnight across northern Shetland.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FCloudy across Orkney with
OL,18,Foccasional rain. A dry day across
OL,19,FShetland with some sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
