OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain clearing on Wednesday. Otherwise
OL,7,Fa dry few days with Orkney seeing the
OL,8,Fbest of the sunshine, Shetland seeing
OL,9,Fmisty low cloud at times. Quite warm.
